            <IconCircleCheckSrc />
            <span>
              Harness the power of OpenAI's GPT models right within your VS Code editor
            </span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <IconCircleCheckSrc />
            <span>Create multiple custom chat agents for different coding scenarios</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <IconCircleCheckSrc />
            <span>Interact with an intelligent AI assistant while maintaining utmost data privacy and security</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <Button />
      </article>
